What's your passion?

Competing on the world's toughest golf course.

Setting a personal triathlon record.

Or making the best deal because you are a gas trading junky.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------

If you can identify with the latter, Dynegydirect is your ticket.
Dynegydirect now offers more than 50 basis swaps across multiple
regions. Follow the instructions below to check them out the next
time you trade online.

But why wait? Go to www.dynegydirect.com to log on to Dynegydirect.



To View Basis Swap Markets
1.  On the Trading Floor, select Customize on the File menu. The
    Configuration dialog box opens.
2.  Click Create to start the Trading Window wizard.
    or
    Select an existing trading window and then click Edit. The Edit
    Trading Floor window opens. Click Add More Products.
3.  In the first wizard pane, type a name for your new window, and
    then click Next.
4.  In the second wizard pane, click the drop-down menu and select
    Trading Window or View Only Window, and then click Next.
5.  In the remaining wizard panes, select the key product attributes
    to narrow the product selection, as needed. In this instance,
    select major and minor commodities, and then select
    Basis Swap deal type.
6.  Click Finish. The Product Configuration dialog box opens.
7.  To add products to the current Trading Window, move them from
    the Available Products list to the Selected Products list using the
    commands provided.
8.  When you finish building the Selected Products list, click Finish.
    The new Trading Window appears on your Trading Floor.

Note: You can see a demonstration of this procedure in the
Dynegydirect tutorial. To load the tutorial, click Tutorial after logging
on to Dynegydirect. Click Trading Floor, Trading Floor Setup, and
then Changing Products in a Window.





















